Class EmailCampaignBase

java.lang.Object

      com.constantcontact.components.emailcampaigns.EmailCampaignBase
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
EmailCampaignRequest, EmailCampaignResponse
public abstract class EmailCampaignBase
extends Component
implements Serializable

Represents a single Email Campaign Base for the Email Campaign Service in Constant Contact.
Response and Request classes extend this.
